{"word":"G3770 - οὐράνιος - ouránios - oo-ran'-ee-os - Heavenly","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">οὐράνιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">ouránios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">oo-ran'-ee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Heavenly</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"பரம - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"heavenly"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3772 - οὐρανός - ouranós - oo-ran-os'/3772\">G3772</a>; <i>celestial</i>, that is, <i>belonging to</i> or <i>coming from</i> the <i>sky:</i> - heavenly.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2032/2032\">G2032</a>, <a href=\"#/G3770/3770\">G3770</a>, <a href=\"#/G3771/3771\">G3771</a>, <a href=\"#/G3772/3772\">G3772</a>"}]}